name: Bite Me Not Ice Cream Badge
description:
Introducing Bite Me Not, he's sad because some giant human bit him. He must be really yummy.

This Alder wood badge is laser cut and has a coated finish. It measures approx 1.7cm wide by 4.2cm high and on the back it has attached a metal safety pin . 

Due to the nature of the wood grain each Ice Cream character badge is unique and may vary slightly from the pictures.

name: Birds in a Tree Painting
description:
Painting of seven birds sitting in a tree, including a penguin somehow.

Acrylic painting on stretched canvas measuring 610 x 200 x 35 mm.

Painting will be securely wrapped and sent by airmail using AUSPost, estimated delivery arrival 3-10 days
